sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client (Svelte)
    participant A as App (Wails Binding)
    participant PM as PlanningManager
    participant PA as PlanAccess
    participant R as Repository (Git)

    Note over C,R: AddRoutine
    C->>A: AddRoutine(themeId, description, targetValue, targetType, unit)
    A->>PM: AddRoutine(themeId, description, targetValue, targetType, unit)
    PM->>PM: Validate inputs (non-empty, valid targetType, positive targetValue)
    PM->>PA: GetThemes()
    PM->>PM: Find theme by ID
    PM->>PM: getMaxRoutineNum() [find next R{n}]
    PM->>PM: Generate routine ID: {themeId}-R{n+1}
    PM->>PM: Append routine to theme
    PM->>PA: SaveTheme(modifiedTheme)
    PA->>R: Begin() -> Stage() -> Commit()
    PM-->>A: *Routine
    A-->>C: *Routine (Wails DTO)

    Note over C,R: UpdateRoutine
    C->>A: UpdateRoutine(routineId, description, currentValue, targetValue, targetType, unit)
    A->>PM: UpdateRoutine(...)
    PM->>PM: Validate inputs
    PM->>PA: GetThemes()
    PM->>PM: findThemeForRoutine() [scan themes]
    PM->>PM: Update all routine fields
    PM->>PA: SaveTheme(modifiedTheme)
    PA->>R: Begin() -> Stage() -> Commit()
    PM-->>A: nil
    A-->>C: nil

    Note over C,R: DeleteRoutine
    C->>A: DeleteRoutine(routineId)
    A->>PM: DeleteRoutine(routineId)
    PM->>PA: GetThemes()
    PM->>PM: findThemeForRoutine() [scan themes]
    PM->>PM: Remove routine from slice
    PM->>PA: SaveTheme(modifiedTheme)
    PA->>R: Begin() -> Stage() -> Commit()
    PM-->>A: nil
    A-->>C: nil
